            "chapterTitle": "Excellence of Standing in Prayer at Night",
            "urn": 1622280,
            "body": "<p>Abu Sa'id and Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with them) reported: The Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) said, \"When a man awakens his wife during the night and they both perform two Rak'ah Salat together, they are recorded among the men and women who celebrate remembrance of Allah.\"<br/><br/><b>[Abu Dawud]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
            "grades": []
        },
